{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_02",
  "title": "プリンセス\nと共同生活",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、はい……分かりました\nみんなにも伝えておきます。それでは、失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.250000095399999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7645.8277862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui001.m4a",
      "text": "今の電話はマネージャーさんからですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4458277862,
      "endTime": 11.5058282535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。貴方達のことを心配していて\n後で様子を見に来るそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7124948343,
      "endTime": 17.4587533792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui002.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーさん、優しいのね\nみなさんも泊まる部屋やお風呂まで用意して下さって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.65458107,
      "endTime": 24.301246929199998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに気にしないで。今はゆっくり休んで\n落ち着いたら改めて帰る方法を考えましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4879137676,
      "endTime": 31.6371655148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう\n知らない場所に飛ばされて不安だったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8329932054,
      "endTime": 35.9729940732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんのような冷静沈着でしっかりした人と\n出会えたのは不幸中の幸いってやつね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1663273017,
      "endTime": 43.352993122899996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "褒め過ぎよ。……まあ、確かに私は\n普段から取り乱さないように心がけているけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5663262845,
      "endTime": 50.7134465695,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7342.947975800002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9213.673715500001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11123.673715499997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-lala001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ～、いいお湯だったよ～。お風呂ありがとー！\nあれ？　何話してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9092742603,
      "endTime": 58.3026065509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "貴方達の今後について……って、どうして裸なのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5092729886,
      "endTime": 63.223512395200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-lala002.m4a",
      "text": "お風呂上がりなんだから裸なのは当たり前だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.419340086,
      "endTime": 66.8822566986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "お風呂を上がったら服を着るのが当たり前よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9860067527,
      "endTime": 70.0794761817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kyui005.m4a",
      "text": "冷静な莉央さんも\nララさんのマイペースには勝てなかったわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2753038724,
      "endTime": 75.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6433.327229799999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "モモちゃん？　こんな所で何をしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4086321195,
      "endTime": 81.4794710954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo001.m4a",
      "text": "泊めてもらったお礼に、植物を植えていたんです\n女子寮ですから防犯対策はしっかりしておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6752987862,
      "endTime": 90.10863485329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "植物って、その木ですか？　普通の木に見えますけど\nこれが防犯対策になるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3086346626,
      "endTime": 98.3234645843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。この宇宙植物は、枝や根が触手のように動いて\n近づいた獲物を捕らえて武装解除させるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5086346626,
      "endTime": 108.2819675446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "おお！　宇宙の植物って凄いですね……！\nこれは面白い悪戯が出来るかもです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4753008206,
      "endTime": 116.5625341732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo003.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとしてこころちゃんってそういうタイプですか？\nふふふ……私達、意外と似ているのかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7753008206,
      "endTime": 127.1686307271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、似たもの同士ということで\n良かったら一緒に悪戯作戦会議しませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3752972603,
      "endTime": 134.11293888089997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "後で、{user}さんが寮に\n来るんですけど、その時に……ごにょごにょごにょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3086305936,
      "endTime": 141.15840380990002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo004.m4a",
      "text": "面白そうですね。それなら思い切って、この植物で……\nごにょごにょごにょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.341963927,
      "endTime": 148.5819577853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "おお～、なるほど！\nふふふ……なんだかモモちゃんとは気が合いそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7752911568,
      "endTime": 155.8911414146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-momo005.m4a",
      "text": "わあ！　美味しそうなお料理が沢山\nこれ全部、莉央さんが作ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.1086316109,
      "endTime": 164.5686257363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。どうですか\nうちの莉央さんは料理上手なんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7752921741,
      "endTime": 169.4446573894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこころが自慢げなのよ\nほら、冷めないうちに食べましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.6419588407,
      "endTime": 175.1667661031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす。……あれ？\nおかずの隣に置いてある、この紫色の物体はなんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3625937939,
      "endTime": 184.80021281249998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-lala003.m4a",
      "text": "それは私が作った料理だよ\n莉央さんのレシピを私なりにアレンジしたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9959271272,
      "endTime": 191.1559334596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "アレンジって、もはや原型をとどめていませんが……\n毒々しい色で、食べるのは勇気がいりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3625998974,
      "endTime": 201.182032919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
